{"tid":1589742,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"推國歌Spotify攻略","createTime":"2019-09-23T11:52:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T02:19:49.000Z","uid":314474,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5de3c1252aa223186e16907c62a69afb481aaff5","tid":1589742,"uid":314474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:52:19.000Z","msg":"依家趁熱鬧快啲推國歌上Spotify Hot 50 HK! <br />\n<br />\n其實都幾簡單，多人分享=上Viral 50 HK，多人聽+加playlist+少skip+add to collection=上Hot 50 HK。上咗Viral之後會多咗人聽，因為有好多人只會不停loop住viral/hot50咁聽歌。就算只係上到Hot 50嘅第#50位，都會因為呢啲只會loop chart嘅人突然多咗好多stream，再上位都唔難。<br />\n<br />\n想上Hot 50好重要好重要係要加首歌入你自己嘅playlist!!! 有咁多個playlist就加晒咁多個，聽果陣可以喺個playlist入面噤黎聽。另一樣好重要嘅就係要聽晒成首歌，千祈唔好skip!!!<br />\n<br />\n臨訓可以開住電腦/電話, 閂聲loop住首歌成晚！<br />\n<br />\n出動啦各位！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/07QvyW4GbifbBSHTX1ksgd?si=y8EvsmXIQtK-SMp22d88Ig\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fopen.spotify.com%2Ftrack%2F07QvyW4GbifbBSHTX1ksgd%3Fsi%3Dy8EvsmXIQtK-SMp22d88Ig&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK67np9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=b47eca60\" target=\"_blank\">https://open.spotify.com/track/07QvyW4GbifbBSHTX1ksgd?si=y8EvsmXIQtK-SMp22d88Ig</a><br />\n<br />\n利申：之前喺唱片公司做，成日就係負責推歌上chart"},{"pid":"0f8e00bcbb1313d7c2b978180bc85469a941e69e","tid":1589742,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:52:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"7541802aa1780d7244a857711776f0f8d8d08f54","tid":1589742,"uid":159136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:57:32.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"278ea2a5d05b3532bbe881fe2deed2dfad979d2c","tid":1589742,"uid":9621,"like":0,"dislike":0,